1
00:00:11,950 --> 00:00:14,340
♪Destiny is so mysterious♪

2
00:00:15,270 --> 00:00:17,540
♪Hazards appear in piles♪

3
00:00:18,370 --> 00:00:20,880
♪Reflected in the mirror of mortal♪

4
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:23,680
♪Reincarnation repeats itself♪

5
00:00:24,530 --> 00:00:27,450
♪I'm so forlorn and no one responds♪

6
00:00:27,830 --> 00:00:30,570
♪Twilight falls on the deserted path♪

7
00:00:30,790 --> 00:00:32,340
♪Beautiful old memories♪

8
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:35,720
♪Echo under the eaves♪

9
00:00:37,110 --> 00:00:39,280
♪I don't want my soul to perish♪

10
00:00:39,280 --> 00:00:40,320
♪Or disappear♪

11
00:00:40,480 --> 00:00:43,260
♪Always live the life, happy or sad♪

12
00:00:43,390 --> 00:00:45,590
♪Get rid of the glory♪

13
00:00:45,590 --> 00:00:46,800
♪Reveal the destiny♪

14
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:49,950
♪Absorb the luck of heaven and earth♪

15
00:00:49,950 --> 00:00:53,070
♪And prosper perfectly♪

16
00:00:53,480 --> 00:00:55,900
♪When young dream chasers♪

17
00:00:55,900 --> 00:00:58,170
♪Travel together♪

18
00:00:58,580 --> 00:01:02,150
♪And shine brightly♪

19
00:01:02,550 --> 00:01:06,080
♪I keep them company for mankind♪

20
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:08,560
♪Waiting to emerge♪

21
00:01:08,850 --> 00:01:12,470
♪However the world changes♪

22
00:01:12,470 --> 00:01:14,920
♪I've never been afraid♪

23
00:01:15,180 --> 00:01:18,620
♪Even if everything collapses in the end♪

24
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:21,860
♪I will hold you in my arms♪

25
00:01:22,670 --> 00:01:27,040
♪Brambles pierce through me♪

26
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:33,580
♪Tears roll down your cheeks♪

27
00:01:33,580 --> 00:01:35,900
=The Last Immortal=

28
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:38,980
=Episode 18=

29
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,680
Jin.

30
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:26,740
Jin.

31
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:31,900
The Sleeping Bug I refined never failed.

32
00:02:32,470 --> 00:02:34,550
You are amazing, Jiu.

33
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:40,020
The Heavenly Matchmaker asked us
to use this gourd to collect Jin's dreams,

34
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:44,390
where we can find his affection ties
from his old memories about love.

35
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:08,960
Got it.

36
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:15,980
Let's go. Come on.

37
00:03:18,150 --> 00:03:18,990
My head hurts.

38
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,340
What are you guys doing here?

39
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,670
I'm passing by.

40
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,460
I came to fetch a book.

41
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,230
I'm here for a tour.

42
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,460
Why are you…

43
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,800
Yin,

44
00:03:39,030 --> 00:03:40,710
why are you holding a gourd
above your head?

45
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,830
They said I looked good in this way.

46
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:50,430
Well,

47
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:52,860
not really.

48
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,300
Why were they all here?

49
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,430
And acting so weird.

50
00:03:58,120 --> 00:04:00,110
They must be keeping
something from me.

51
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,990
Go to Bainiao Island right now
and report to His Lordship

52
00:04:04,310 --> 00:04:07,360
that Princess Hua Shu went to the dangerous
secret area of the Inferno Sea alone

53
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,990
to look for the parasol tree
for Immortal Gu Jin.

54
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,080
Let him send help to…

55
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:10,920
Hongque,

56
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,230
what did you say?

57
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,870
Your Lordship,

58
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:17,960
you…

59
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,580
Actually…

60
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:24,630
Actually, Her Highness knew
you were looking for the parasol tree,

61
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,710
so she's been keeping an eye on it.

62
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:29,750
A few days ago, she finally found a clue
from an ancient book in our clan.

63
00:04:29,990 --> 00:04:31,870
But the secret area
of the Inferno Sea is too dangerous.

64
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,200
I was going to stop her from going,

65
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:37,580
but it's my fault
that I sent the wrong message

66
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:41,550
and made Yin late
for welcoming the Nether King.

67
00:04:41,550 --> 00:04:44,870
But, Her Highness took
full responsibility for it

68
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,780
and wanted to make up
for the mistake whatsoever,

69
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:48,420
so she went to the secret area alone.

70
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:54,710
Hua Shu really feels guilty
about Yin's matter?

71
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,030
Yes.

72
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,560
(Fine.)

73
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:03,020
(After all, she took the risk
to help me look for the parasol tree.)

74
00:05:03,510 --> 00:05:04,630
(I can't sit back and do nothing.)

75
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:11,580
I'll go find her.

76
00:05:13,100 --> 00:05:15,580
(Secret Area of the Inferno Sea)

77
00:05:27,950 --> 00:05:29,540
(There really is a parasol tree.)

78
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,760
Immortal spirit.

79
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,150
This is

80
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:58,420
the tinder vine
that'd spit fire when in danger.

81
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:05,070
Your Highness.

82
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,710
(Oh, no. It's blood-sucking sand,)

83
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,420
(the fieriest flame spiritual stone.)

84
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:07,520
Run.

85
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:16,150
Are you okay?

86
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:17,230
Sorry, Jin.

87
00:07:17,830 --> 00:07:20,220
I just wanted to help you find
Feng Yin's immortal spirit.

88
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:23,510
I didn't expect the tinder vine
could be this powerful.

89
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,390
(He's a True God indeed.)

90
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:05,780
(His power improved rapidly
in such a short time.)

91
00:08:12,830 --> 00:08:14,780
(Impart Wisdom to Offspring)
You bunch of bullies. Let me go.

92
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,110
Let me go.

93
00:08:16,110 --> 00:08:17,270
Let go of me.

94
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,400
Do you hear me?

95
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,310
No matter what, I will not kiss…

96
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,580
Today, whether you want

97
00:08:27,270 --> 00:08:31,270
or not, it's not up to you.

98
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:44,060
That's enough.

99
00:08:44,790 --> 00:08:47,150
Is that how Jin thinks of me?

100
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:52,350
Yin, good for you.

101
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:54,060
You threw yourself right at him.

102
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:56,270
Gu Jin is such a narcissist.

103
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:09,820
What happened

104
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:11,900
to the gourd?

105
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:16,200
I've sensed that
the dreamer's affection ties

106
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:18,660
(The Heavenly Matchmaker)
haven't been destroyed yet.

107
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,770
But usually,

108
00:09:20,770 --> 00:09:25,470
my spellworking could've summoned
the affection ties back right away.

109
00:09:25,790 --> 00:09:27,900
So, what should we do now?

110
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:30,300
If I'm right,

111
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:34,540
his affection ties are sealed
by some sort of powerful force.

112
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:37,940
We need to find
his affection ties back as soon

113
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,150
as possible.

114
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:40,300
If it's too late,

115
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:42,540
he may develop affections
towards someone else,

116
00:09:42,790 --> 00:09:46,510
and the old affection ties
can never be restored.

117
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:47,860
Where can we find them then?

118
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:51,020
The Three Realms are huge.
We don't know where to start.

119
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,180
I don't know either,

120
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:57,500
but throughout the world, there are very few
tools that can remove affection ties.

121
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:02,300
Among them, the Memory-erasing Flute
of Daze Mountain works the best.

122
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:04,940
Daze Mountain?

123
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,800
Sir,

124
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,180
are you sure it's Daze Mountain?

125
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,510
Daze Mountain?

126
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:16,510
Isn't that the sect that Yin
and Gu Jin belong to?

127
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:18,750
Then there's no question

128
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:21,510
that someone removed Gu Jin's affection ties
with the Memory-erasing Flute.

129
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:24,990
So, my senior brothers
are all aware of it.

130
00:10:25,790 --> 00:10:28,110
They don't want me
to be with Gu Jin either.

131
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,040
Yin,

132
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,590
it doesn't matter
whether they know or not.

133
00:10:33,870 --> 00:10:36,660
What matters is that we have a clue now.

134
00:10:39,510 --> 00:10:40,590
Yin,

135
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,560
don't worry.

136
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:46,080
I'll go to Daze Mountain right now
and help you find Gu Jin's affection ties back.

137
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,870
He'll be your lover again in no time.

138
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:53,580
(Heavenly Palace, the Immortal Realm)

139
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,540
Your Highness, have a good rest.

140
00:10:59,150 --> 00:10:59,990
I'll leave now.

141
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:03,020
Thank you, Jin. Take care.

142
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,060
Your Highness. Your Highness.

143
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:11,310
Your Lordship, I'll go get some medicine.

144
00:11:11,310 --> 00:11:13,230
Could you please watch
Her Highness for a while?

145
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:14,590
Go ahead.

146
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:15,710
I'll be here.

147
00:11:16,870 --> 00:11:17,990
Thank you, Your Lordship.

148
00:11:30,790 --> 00:11:31,820
Sorry, Jin.

149
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:33,990
Instead of helping you,

150
00:11:34,510 --> 00:11:37,020
I caused you trouble.

151
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:40,020
Your Highness,
you got hurt for helping me.

152
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:42,180
How could you cause me trouble?

153
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:50,390
Your Highness, you are badly injured.
Why are you being so hard on yourself?

154
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:56,420
I've got used to a small injury like this.

155
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,390
You know what, Jin?

156
00:11:59,390 --> 00:12:02,470
Actually, I envy Yin a lot

157
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:05,350
that she has a senior brother
like you to protect her.

158
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,270
Unlike her,

159
00:12:08,910 --> 00:12:10,020
my father is old,

160
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:13,060
and my brother is incapable.

161
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:16,660
I had to learn to be independent
since I was little.

162
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:21,510
I know I did a lot of selfish things
for Bainiao Island.

163
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,390
You have every right
to be angry with me.

164
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:25,320
- But…
- Your Highness,

165
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:29,230
I've told you,
it's all water under the bridge.

166
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,820
Let's not talk about that anymore.

167
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,160
Jin,

168
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:42,020
you must hate people like me, don't you?

169
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,630
If I had a choice,

170
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:48,870
I'd rather be innocent
and carefree like Yin is,

171
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,820
doing whatever I want to do

172
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:53,350
and going after the one I love.

173
00:12:54,270 --> 00:12:58,150
Your Highness, you should
relax and be who you are.

174
00:12:58,390 --> 00:13:00,110
Yin doesn't have
my protection all the time.

175
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:03,060
Instead, a lot of times,
she's the one who helps me.

176
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:08,150
I see that you are tired. I'll leave now.

177
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:10,230
Your Highness, rest well.

178
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:23,470
(I didn't expect it'd be this hard
to win Gu Jin's heart back.)

179
00:13:25,150 --> 00:13:27,420
(It's not as easy
to manipulate him as before.)

180
00:13:34,860 --> 00:13:39,820
(Clouds Form over Mountains)

181
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:42,970
We need to find
his affection ties back as soon

182
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,180
as possible.

183
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:45,150
If it's too late,

184
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:47,510
he may develop affections
towards someone else,

185
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:52,020
and the old affection ties
can never be restored.

186
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:57,340
(Clouds Form over Mountains)

187
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:26,990
Yin, when will you go back
to Daze Mountain to get the Flute?

188
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,540
I need more time to think about it.

189
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:33,100
You've been wanting to help Gu Jin
find his affection ties back.

190
00:14:33,100 --> 00:14:34,940
And now, you finally have a clue.

191
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,470
Why are you hesitating?

192
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:42,110
Because I feel like I'm the only one
who wants this relationship to happen.

193
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:46,230
I don't have my senior brothers' support.

194
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:52,230
I'm afraid they wouldn't
give me the Flute.

195
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,630
But, who you love
should be your own decision.

196
00:14:58,080 --> 00:15:01,630
Does it matter whether or not
you have their support?

197
00:15:03,670 --> 00:15:06,590
If you are destined
to get hurt from this relationship,

198
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:08,060
will you regret it?

199
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,110
I won't.

200
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,510
Then there you go.

201
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,350
You should follow your heart then.

202
00:15:17,550 --> 00:15:21,230
Perhaps, because of what happened
between Wan Yue and Xian Zhu,

203
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:26,300
my senior brothers don't want Jin
to go through the same.

204
00:15:26,870 --> 00:15:29,780
Who would know
what will happen in the future?

205
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,430
Besides, it's up to Gu Jin

206
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,630
what he wants to experience

207
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,630
and what he doesn't.

208
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:37,780
The others have no right
to make a decision for him.

209
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:41,750
Even so, they still
wouldn't give me the Flute.

210
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:45,300
Three-life Stone will figure out a way.

211
00:15:45,670 --> 00:15:46,540
Think about it,

212
00:15:46,910 --> 00:15:49,710
she can go into anywhere
in the Three Realms to match people up.

213
00:15:49,710 --> 00:15:51,510
You think Daze Mountain can stop her?

214
00:15:56,550 --> 00:15:57,900
Stop worrying.

215
00:16:01,460 --> 00:16:04,860
(Entrance, Daze Mountain)

216
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:40,820
(Clouds Form over Mountains)

217
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:51,160
Your Lordship.

218
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:52,820
Immortal Gu Jin.

219
00:16:53,390 --> 00:16:56,110
I heard you've been
taking care of my daughter. Thank you.

220
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,320
Don't.

221
00:16:57,630 --> 00:16:58,990
She got hurt for helping me.

222
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:00,320
I should look after her.

223
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:02,920
Your Lordship.

224
00:17:08,110 --> 00:17:10,700
Your Lordship, the Energy Protection Arrow
has been forged successfully.

225
00:17:11,920 --> 00:17:12,760
Good.

226
00:17:14,270 --> 00:17:15,630
Then I'll take my leave.

227
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:16,760
Alright.

228
00:17:17,750 --> 00:17:18,590
Let's go.

229
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:37,950
Leave us.

230
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:39,800
Yes.

231
00:17:54,550 --> 00:17:57,630
Gu Jin humiliated you on Bainiao Island.

232
00:17:58,240 --> 00:18:00,390
Why are you trying to draw him over?

233
00:18:00,420 --> 00:18:02,870
It's not guaranteed that I can become
one of the five Immortal Lords.

234
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:05,310
It's better to be fully prepared.

235
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:08,870
Shu,

236
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,500
I have an idea,

237
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:16,390
but I need you to do one thing.

238
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:26,670
This arrow contains
mighty spiritual power.

239
00:18:26,670 --> 00:18:29,740
I'm sure it can protect
the finger bone of Lord Zhen Yi.

240
00:18:31,590 --> 00:18:35,350
Later, I'll personally escort the Arrow
into the Secret Storeroom.

241
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:37,800
Yan Shuang,

242
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:38,910
Yin,

243
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,260
you two forged the Arrow.

244
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,030
You can go with me.

245
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,560
Yes.

246
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:56,630
This arrow looks exactly
like the Energy Protection Arrow.

247
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:58,910
Before the display
of the finger bone of Lord Zhen Yi,

248
00:18:58,910 --> 00:19:03,110
the Energy Protection Arrow
will be kept in the Secret Storeroom.

249
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:06,390
You want to replace the Arrow
with this one?

250
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:07,480
That's right.

251
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:10,330
But it takes the permission document
to open the Secret Storeroom.

252
00:19:10,330 --> 00:19:13,390
Lan Feng and Wind Lord each hold half.

253
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:17,310
It's easy to get the half
that Wind Lord has,

254
00:19:17,550 --> 00:19:20,700
but it's quite difficult
to sneak in Lan Feng's Lingyu Hall.

255
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:25,900
So, I need you to think of a way
to get the half that Lan Feng has.

256
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:28,030
Open the Secret Storeroom
and replace the Arrow.

257
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:29,870
Wind Lord,

258
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:33,940
Lingyu Hall and the Hall of Wind should each
hold half of the permission document.

259
00:19:33,990 --> 00:19:36,500
The gate of the Secret Storeroom can't
be opened until the two halves combined.

260
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:37,500
Yes, Your Majesty.

261
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:40,700
Our Hall of Wind is taking
the night shift tonight.

262
00:19:40,920 --> 00:19:45,030
I'll ask someone from the Hall of Wind
to take the half of the document

263
00:19:45,510 --> 00:19:47,150
