of the South Sea.

289
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:12,150
Even if the Demon Realm
gets the Nirvana Wheel back,

290
00:21:12,680 --> 00:21:14,630
it won't do the Immortal Realm any harm.

291
00:21:15,240 --> 00:21:18,590
