299
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:58,820
(Secret Storeroom)

300
00:22:08,310 --> 00:22:09,310
Greetings, Your Majesty.

301
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,870
According to the rules,

302
00:22:11,030 --> 00:22:13,390
