380
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:26,860
It looks a lot like the Nirvana Wheel.

381
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:27,950
Have you seen it, Aunt?

382
00:28:27,950 --> 00:28:28,790
No.

383
00:28:28,790 --> 00:28:30,390
I came from this route,

384
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:33,150
