and I don't think that's true.

398
00:29:07,880 --> 00:29:10,570
I just need some time to confirm the details.

399
00:29:10,570 --> 00:29:12,430
There's no need
to investigate this matter further.

400
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:14,250
If it's not the Immortal Realm,
then who else could it be?

401
00:29:14,270 --> 00:29:15,390
Do you think they would

402
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:18,260
