431
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,350
but due to the conflicts between
the Immortal and Demon Realms,

432
00:30:55,680 --> 00:30:57,660
it had been suspended for hundreds of years.

433
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,940
