435
00:31:03,110 --> 00:31:06,280
hoping to resolve the conflicts with the Demon
and Nether Realms,

436
00:31:06,920 --> 00:31:10,740
promoting peace for generations to come.

437
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:45,940
